	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ay<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /> Soy un desastre.<delay20 /> <anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Esto no es
